OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Harry
OL,4,CHoworth
OL,6,FHarry Howorth, Aged 102, King's
OL,7,FShropshire Light Infantry
OL,9,FInterviewed 18 February 2024
OL,11,FDied 18 April 2024
OL,13,FAmong the first troops to arrive at
OL,14,FSword Beach early on the morning of D-
OL,15,FDay, Harry Howorth was the third
OL,16,Fperson to step from his landing craft
OL,17,Fas it hit the beach.
OL,19,FThe vessel had walkways on each side.
