OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Harry
OL,4,CHoworth
OL,6,FHe said: "You ran down the steps into
OL,7,Fthe water, as that's what you were
OL,8,Fsupposed to do.
OL,10,F"But the ladder, the walkway, a sailor
OL,11,Fwas holding the rope, taking all the
OL,12,Fflak.
OL,14,F"He didn't last long, so consequently
OL,15,Fthe ramp I was on went down because
OL,16,Fhe'd been shot, and it broke off.
OL,18,F"So I ended up in the water.
