OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Harry
OL,4,CHoworth
OL,6,F"I looked at the boat coming in on the
OL,7,Fright hand side of me," he said. "I
OL,8,Fsaw a hole come in the side of the
OL,9,Fship and two seconds or so after there
OL,10,Fwas a big bang and I would have
OL,11,Fthought everyone on board that ship
OL,12,Fwas dead.
OL,14,F"I got on the beach.
OL,16,F"We were running beside each other and
OL,17,Fthere was flak and strafing and the
OL,18,Fnoise was terrific.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
