OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Harry
OL,4,CHoworth
OL,6,F"We took cover inside a burnt-out half
OL,7,Ftrack and crouched behind there. More
OL,8,For less to get our mind focused.
OL,10,F"And I saw a regiment three abreast
OL,11,Frunning down the street towards Bayeux
OL,12,Fand I thought 'that will be our lot.'
OL,13,FAnd then I realised I had been a fool
OL,14,Fand went the wrong way."
OL,16,F"I wasn't scared at the time - about
OL,17,Ftwo days after I landed I was scared
OL,18,Fthen.
